| AdPolicyHints | 1.2.840.113556.1.4.223 | Enforces the password history length constraint during password set | S | [LDAP_SERVER_POLICY_HINTS_OID](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/hh128228.aspx) | AD |
